	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Ghuar Mota&lt;/strong&gt; in the Kutch region of Gujarat is the westernmost point in India.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Tamilnadu&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;is the southernmost state of India.
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Indira Point &lt;/strong&gt;is&amp;nbsp;the Southernmost point of land in the territory of India.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
