	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Kanyakumari &lt;/strong&gt;is the southernmost town in mainland India.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/additional-information-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Additional Information&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The mainland of India extends between &lt;strong&gt;8&amp;deg;4&amp;#39;N and 37&amp;deg;6&amp;#39;N latitudes.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The latitude of the northernmost point of India, nearest to minutes is &lt;strong&gt;37&amp;deg; 6&amp;#39;.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The latitude of the southernmost point of India, nearest to minutes is &lt;strong&gt;8&amp;deg;4&amp;#39;.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The mainland of India extends between &lt;strong&gt;68&amp;deg;7&amp;#39;E and 97&amp;deg;25&amp;#39;E longitudes.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The equator represents the &lt;strong&gt;zero degrees latitude.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The equator is the longest latitude.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;All latitudes are parallel to the equator.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

